name: WhoisCool
0:
”Alexa, tell me who is cool”
”Alexa, tell me who is cool, change name”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: me who is cool
des: Ask 'Alexa, tell me who is cool?' to train Alexa to remember any name. Then ask 'Alexa, tell me who is cool?' and she will repeat your name back to you. To change the name later, say 'Alexa, tell me who is cool, change name'.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
